<h1>Shipping Policy</h1>
<p>We ship across India with delivery times ranging from 3–7 business days based on your location.</p>

<h2>Shipping Charges</h2>
<p>Shipping is free for orders above ₹499. For others, a flat ₹49 shipping fee applies.</p>

<h2>Tracking</h2>
<p>Once your order is dispatched, you’ll receive an email with a tracking link.</p>
